      "content": "i dont think there are any other patterns to look at. i've looked at everything. it's not about some \"strategy\" or a \"support system.\" it's just the weight of it all. the loop is just gravity pulling me back down every single time. at some point, you just have to accept that the loop is inevitable and the only way to stop the noise is to just let go.",
